0: jdbc:hive2://localhost:10000> -- Create External Table for PART-SHIPPED-BY (PARTSUPP)
0: jdbc:hive2://localhost:10000> CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE IF NOT EXISTS partsupp (
. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .>     PS_PARTKEY STRING,
. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .>     PS_SUPPKEY STRING,
. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .>     PS_AVAILQTY INT,     
. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .>     PS_SUPPLYCOST DOUBLE,
. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .>     PS_COMMENT STRING    
. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .> )
. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .> ROW FORMAT DELIMITED
. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .> FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|'
. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .> STORED AS TEXTFILE
. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .> LOCATION '/user/hive/warehouse/task4/partsupp'
. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .> TBLPROPERTIES ("skip.header.line.count"="1");
